I could lose my job.

253
00:14:12,551 --> 00:14:14,186
And I can't afford
to lose my job.

254
00:14:17,957 --> 00:14:19,158
Be straight with me, okay?

255
00:14:19,191 --> 00:14:21,126
All right, go ahead.
What do you wanna know?

256
00:14:21,160 --> 00:14:23,229
The last information we have
is from the Reynold school.

257
00:14:23,262 --> 00:14:24,964
That's his last placement?
Yeah.

258
00:14:24,997 --> 00:14:27,333
Then where did the authorities
get the idea that David

