261
00:14:31,136 --> 00:14:32,404
To protect him.
From what?

262
00:14:32,438 --> 00:14:34,406
The bastards at
the Reynold school.

263
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:36,242
There are other programs.

264
00:14:36,275 --> 00:14:37,543
We have been there.

265
00:14:37,576 --> 00:14:39,712
