that I expected
a much older man.

336
00:18:28,474 --> 00:18:30,175
[CHUCKLES]

337
00:18:30,209 --> 00:18:32,444
Do you like that?
[CHUCKLES]

338
00:18:32,478 --> 00:18:33,946
