355
00:19:42,481 --> 00:19:45,517
[LAUGHTER]

356
00:19:52,057 --> 00:19:53,759
At ease, soldier.

357
00:19:54,793 --> 00:19:57,429
John, this is my sister
Sally Goodson.

358
00:19:57,462 --> 00:19:58,797
Sally, this is John Nils.

359
00:19:59,798 --> 00:20:01,833
Hello.
Hi.

360
00:20:01,867 --> 00:20:04,303
How are you?
Hi. You want a drink?

361
00:20:04,336 --> 00:20:05,971
Yes.

362
00:20:06,004 --> 00:20:07,439
I'll get the waiter.

363
00:20:07,472 --> 00:20:08,974
Is that what you did
to you hair?

364
00:20:09,007 --> 00:20:11,376
I couldn't decide between
