371
00:20:22,854 --> 00:20:24,289
Yes, ma'am.

372
00:20:27,559 --> 00:20:29,394
Isn't it a beautiful day?

373
00:20:29,428 --> 00:20:31,363
Oh, it must be 75 degrees
out there.

374
00:20:31,396 --> 00:20:33,632
You know, I just love it
when there's that little...

375
00:20:33,665 --> 00:20:36,835
Christmas, you know,
there's that little nip
in the air, but...

376
00:20:36,868 --> 00:20:39,071
Ah, still...
She always wanted to be
a weather girl,

377
00:20:39,104 --> 00:20:40,639
