385
00:21:04,062 --> 00:21:06,832
A nod and a grunt is not
what I consider talking.

386
00:21:06,865 --> 00:21:10,836
Now, when he gets back here,
I wanna see some charm,
some sparkle, some vivacity.

387
00:21:10,869 --> 00:21:12,838
Hire a clown.
I already got one.

388
00:21:12,871 --> 00:21:14,373
Just relax.

389
00:21:14,406 --> 00:21:15,741
