Make up your mind.

390
00:21:15,774 --> 00:21:18,043
You want a relaxed mute,
or frenzied debutant?

391
00:21:20,512 --> 00:21:22,981
[SIGHS DEEPLY]

392
00:21:42,534 --> 00:21:43,735
