I am so uptight that I won't do
my Oprah Winfrey imitation.

396
00:21:52,411 --> 00:21:55,080
[JOHN LAUGHS]

397
00:21:55,113 --> 00:21:57,449
I haven't been in
a social situation
with a man...

398
00:21:58,684 --> 00:22:00,686
