I've ever had.
[LAUGHING]

406
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:16,835
That's because
you're so funny.

407
00:22:18,170 --> 00:22:20,005
Justine?

408
00:22:20,038 --> 00:22:22,407
The Governor called,
your apartment came through.

409
00:22:23,175 --> 00:22:24,710
They're not here.

410
00:22:24,743 --> 00:22:26,645
