411
00:22:26,678 --> 00:22:27,746
It's very nice.

412
00:22:27,779 --> 00:22:29,781
Mm-hmm. Have you had
your tetanus shots?

413
00:22:30,082 --> 00:22:31,817
[CHUCKLES]

414
00:22:31,850 --> 00:22:34,152
No, this, this place
is for living, it's not
for showing off.

415
00:22:34,186 --> 00:22:36,621
That's right.
We're definitely
downwardly mobile.

416
00:22:37,189 --> 00:22:39,458
Can I get you a drink?

417
00:22:39,491 --> 00:22:41,727
I have some cheap gin
and some flat tonic.

418
00:22:41,760 --> 00:22:42,894
