upstairs.

421
00:22:49,034 --> 00:22:51,470
Oh, the penthouse.

422
00:22:51,503 --> 00:22:53,472
Whoo-whoo-whoo.

423
00:22:53,505 --> 00:22:57,743
It's just a little balcony
really, but I can see
the new store from there. I...

424
00:22:57,776 --> 00:23:00,679
