another store?

425
00:23:00,712 --> 00:23:02,814
Oh, maybe a couple of times.
[CHUCKLES]
[CHUCKLES]

426
00:23:03,148 --> 00:23:04,750
Well...

427
00:23:04,783 --> 00:23:05,951
